    :field public shared _false←{⍵⊣⍵.⎕DF'false'}⎕NS ''   ⍝ same definition as in #.JSON

    _used←'' ⍝ keep track of what's been used

    ∇ Make
      :Access public
      :Implements constructor :Base
      MakeCommon
    ∇

    ∇ Make1 req
      :Access public
